Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:13.25,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇滚星球 摇滚星球 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:18.52,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的摇滚行星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:33.62,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀的银河 以目光穿越
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:48.92,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你燃烧的心 无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:51.62,op2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由太阳算起的第三颗星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:55.82,op2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你响起恋爱之铃 我敲打着恋爱之鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:01:02.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇滚星球 摇滚星球 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:08.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的摇滚行星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:15.74,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇滚行星 我们摇滚在此行星 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:22.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的摇滚行星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次初恋 会回到过去吗 拉姆和阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得收在一起的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是13岁生日拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这虽然像但也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆姐 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 找东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳坠的另一半怎么也找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 是像这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心型且有裂痕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是拉姆姐这么盛妆到底要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被邀请去终太郎家的宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到这个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好戴一个去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天 听见了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好、我也想去参加派对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 找到另一个耳坠送过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部把它搬开应该找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么门呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下拼上命也要找到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐以及先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚为我所宠爱的杰士菲妮的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请诸位这么多人参加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂终太郎我真是感激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的杰士菲妮也该出嫁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面颊的光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿润的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是含苞待放之时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起两年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的、我还以为是什么派对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没必耍盛妆而来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这么好吃的东西一般不太容易吃到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会给个袋子打包回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是拉姆姐所找耳坠的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到相同的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?拉姆姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放回原来的盒子 锁好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那链子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能再打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链子?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是耳坠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小天知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 我特地送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会翻出那旧东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和我一对的链子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是恋爱的符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要想见到对方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快打开链盒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不管分开多远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链子便互相牵引马上就能见到面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷 混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想了起来真是个恶梦之恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开我玩笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 你今晚是天上所掉落美丽之星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芙萝蒂在你面前也相形失色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芙萝蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又放着拉姆姐不管在偷腥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人没让你来你偏冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下去 退下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家正在好好享受白吃白喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别烦人 真困拢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无关的人闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的小孩真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可要火了哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是拉姆姐最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是阿雷的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在很重要的箱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆姐毕竞是个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷是拉姆姐的初恋情人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竞还是怀念的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明菜小姐 下次要不要一起去滑冰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣子也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是去郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优要看电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者去听音乐会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎么一副恐怖的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们最适合珍珠般的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 你又找其他女孩子搭讪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没资格责备我偷腥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆子不小嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定每晚抱着这链子做着粉色的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做无谓的辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 你能走的路只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不听你的 去尼姑庵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把头剃光去尼姑庵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还说是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 混蛋 为何打开链子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又为什么阿雷会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅 真迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互吸引的链子?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦!你把这东西当宝贝收藏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗、是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那东西丢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法丢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这链子有另一个可怕的机能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的机能?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么样呢 拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是恋情快破裂之时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将链子合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,则爱情将会恢复的可怕机能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不注意丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某种巧合下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定进入阿雷肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不是在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情能恢复之事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 被他知道就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静 说话声音太大会被听见的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那呆子说他会懂?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!另一条链子!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要将那夺取丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用担心会破镜重圆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐 包在我身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好开心 达令吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子 谁吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星传给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 你去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有这个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令为何要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不明白这个状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼者 给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自私的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不喜欢面堂家的派对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会发生什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美丽的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得能见到阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我能见到阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我能见到阿雷 奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我能见到阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本觉得自己有点窝囊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没想到能在你家喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是世界上最幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的链子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的达令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然随身带着拉姆的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱的人只有阿兰你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆为何来到此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打开链子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个拥有的人 不管在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能马上到达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天客人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝个茶 慢慢聊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说是恢复爱情的链子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好追来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰完全搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了你 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这链子是以前拉姆小姐\N送给阿雷的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使爱情破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要将两人的链子合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会有破镜重圆之机能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这卑鄙小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想和阿雷重修旧好吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看我正努力不让链子复原吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄坏不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放手阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这件事是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用那哀伤的眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样对我 阿兰我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到远处破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不可以阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以追
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走 阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星传给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这卑鄙之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 阿雷好吃的饭团哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用石头也打坏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寂静之夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 年轻人真吵呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然追我而来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴呀 阿兰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电桌猫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我蛮搭配的嘛 阿兰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:23:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会坏了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有恢复旧爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子 我早就知道会如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没坏会怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着五月之风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.85,0:23:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到友引町的一对父女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热热的刚泡咖啡是要加酒的或是美式的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春老伯登场
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀!梦中之咖啡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.68,0:24:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:28.68,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我独自的漫步在雨中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.68,0:24:31.73,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在从前...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.38,0:24:36.25,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你出现时那一切是寒冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.25,0:24:39.32,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还要故作姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.92,0:24:43.85,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 宝贝 你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.86,0:24:47.82,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你改变了我的一切 哦！宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.82,0:24:50.03,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能否再受感动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:56.27,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使每天更好...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.27,0:25:00.35,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天我沉浸在爱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.35,0:25:04.21,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.21,0:25:08.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天你充满在我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.05,0:25:11.84,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梦中你使其真实
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.84,0:25:15.56,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天你带来阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.56,0:25:19.63,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在整晚中追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.63,0:25:23.30,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天都是我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.30,0:25:27.86,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期望你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
